      <title>南航加入 C919 喷气式客机交易狂潮，与竞争对手双寡头垄断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-southern-joins-deal-frenzy-for-c919-jet-to-rival-duopoly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国南方航空公司表示，将购买 100 架中国商飞 C919 喷气式飞机，这增强了该本土飞机制造商近期与老牌波音公司和空中客车公司争夺市场份额的连续订单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-southern-joins-deal-frenzy-for-c919-jet-to-rival-duopoly</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 12:13:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
